title: #92Noon! Thielen's MN Covid Relief Radiothon Show!
description: Adam Thielen is essentially the co-host with PA on a show that includes Kirk Cousins, Zach Parise, Lindsay Whalen, Ben Leber in studio, Josh Duhamel, Mardy Fish, Mrs Thielen and Cordarrelle Patterson! Absolute blast, with donations supporting Covid-19 relief efforts in Minnesota!
